         <pb n="1"/>

         <div type="poem">
            <head xml:id="M4.heading1" rend="underline">Pakistan, they said to her</head>
            <lg>
               <l xml:id="M4.1">But what was Pakistan?</l>
               <l xml:id="M4.2">A <subst>
                     <del change="#change-b">country</del>
                     <add place="below" change="#change-b"><subst>
                           <del>gathering</del>
                           <add place="above">massing</add>
                        </subst></add>
                  </subst>, a bolt-hole, a road of bone?</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l xml:id="M4.3">In the <add change="#change-b" place="inline">re</add>folding of
                  saris </l>
               <l xml:id="M4.4">and the salting of lassi — </l>
               <l xml:id="M4.5" rend="right">Pakistan</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l xml:id="M4.6">Along the length of a plait,</l>
               <l xml:id="M4.7">in the journey of an ant — </l>
               <l xml:id="M4.8" rend="right">Pakistan</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l xml:id="M4.9">It held out its different sets of arms</l>
               <l xml:id="M4.10">offered its hard or soft embrace</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l xml:id="M4.11"><del change="#change-b">The innumerable Pakistans</del></l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l xml:id="M4.12">To the East and West</l>
               <l xml:id="M4.13">the <subst>
                     <del change="#change-b">promised land</del>
                     <add place="below" change="#change-b">Pakistan</add>
                  </subst> persisted</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l xml:id="M4.14">but it wasn't half empty,</l>
               <l xml:id="M4.15"><subst>
                     <del>and what</del>
                     <add place="above">all</add>
                  </subst> there was couldn't be past aid</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l xml:id="M4.16"><del>Pakistan raging on subdued</del></l>
               <l xml:id="M4.17">a restless tiger, <subst>
                     <del>lying in wait</del>
                     <add>Pakistan lay in wait</add>
                  </subst>
               </l>
            </lg>
            <lg change="#change-b">
               <l xml:id="M4.18">Would there really be marches</l>
               <l xml:id="M4.19">the other way</l>
            </lg>
            <lg change="#change-b #change-a">
               <l xml:id="M4.20"><del change="#change-a #change-b">Pakistan
                     <unclear>if</unclear></del></l>
               <l xml:id="M4.21">Where would <subst change="#change-b">
                     <del>she</del>
                     <add place="above">they</add>
                  </subst> live<lb/> and work? </l>
               <l xml:id="M4.22">How would they <supplied>live and work</supplied></l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l xml:id="M4.23"><del change="#change-b">A rest<subst change="#change-a">
                        <del>less</del>
                        <add>ive</add>
                     </subst> tiger, Pakistan lay in wait</del></l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l xml:id="M4.24" change="#change-b">At what would they work?</l>
            </lg>

         </div>


